  "track": "Security",
  "speakerId": "spk-duke",
  "roomId": "room-hall-a",
  "startTime": "2026-10-16T14:00:00",
  "durationMinutes": 50
}

### Demo 4 — Read endpoints are @PermitAll — no token needed
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Accept: application/json

### Demo 5 — Request Signature (HMAC) → see http/signatures.http
### NOTE: the @SignatureRequired binding is currently not applied to any
### endpoint. To run this demo live, annotate one resource method with
### @SignatureRequired. See signatures.http for details.


